  "/tikz/row sep": {
    "type": "key",
    "signatureHtml": "<kbd>/tikz/row sep=</kbd>⟨<i>spacing list</i>⟩",
    "defaultHtml": "(no default)",
    "snippetHtml": "<p> This option works like <code>column sep</code>, only for rows. Here, too, you can specify whether the space is added between the lower end of the first row and the upper end of the second row, or whether the space is computed between the origins of the two rows. </p>",
